.TH al_set_new_display_refresh_rate 3 "" "Allegro reference manual"
.SH NAME
.PP
al_set_new_display_refresh_rate - Allegro 5 API
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
#include\ <allegro5/allegro.h>

void\ al_set_new_display_refresh_rate(int\ refresh_rate)
\f[]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Sets the refresh rate to use when creating new displays on the calling
thread.
If the refresh rate is not available, al_create_display(3) will fail.
A list of modes with refresh rates can be found with
al_get_num_display_modes(3) and al_get_display_mode(3).
.PP
The default setting is zero (don\[aq]t care).
.SH SEE ALSO
.PP
al_get_new_display_refresh_rate(3)
